Name: Verify if login API is working.
Description: This test case verifies that a user can log in successfully using the Login API.

Name: Verify if forgot password API is working.
Description: This test case verifies that the forgot password functionality works correctly.

Name: Verify updating profile with invalid token should return Unauthorized
Description: This test case verifies that updating a user profile with an invalid token returns a 401 Unauthorized status.

Name: Verify retrieving profile with expired token should return Unauthorized
Description: This test case verifies that retrieving a user profile with an expired token returns a 401 Unauthorized status.

Name: Verify retrieving profile with invalid token should return Unauthorized
Description: This test case verifies that retrieving a user profile with an invalid token returns a 401 Unauthorized status.

Name: Verify the account creation functionality.
Description: This test case verifies that a new user account can be created successfully using the SignUp API.

Name: Verify updating profile with empty payload should return Bad Request
Description: This test case verifies that updating a user profile with an empty payload returns a 400 Bad Request status.

Name: Verify the user profile retrieval functionality.
Description: This test case verifies that a user profile can be retrieved successfully using the User Management API.

Name: Verify the user profile update functionality.
Description: This test case verifies that a user profile can be updated successfully using the User Management API.
